{"tid":2148615,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"清潔工阻差辦公判社服　律政司申請覆核改判囚被拒兼付訟費","createTime":"2020-08-10T04:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T04:44:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b5783ba17fc2ce3bcd1a63e76d90a65fc82c19ba","tid":2148615,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7950&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YsvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=89fc905f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7950</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第四庭<br />\n#黃國輝裁判官 #覆核聆訊 <br />\n👤何(49) #0805深水埗<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n<br />\n🛑因索取背景報告及社會服務令報告，已還柙12天，原審判160小時社會服務令<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n控辯雙方早前已就刑期覆核，向法庭提交書面陳詞，今天口頭陳述補充<br />\n<br />\n📌<br />\n今天控方回應辯方書面陳述，指本案罪行嚴重，且本案發生在去年6月之後，當時有很多針對警方行為。控方認為就阻嚇性方面，法庭應給予更大比重。考慮被告背景及過往刑事記錄，建議判處2個月即時監禁，以增加公眾阻嚇性。<br />\n<br />\n📌辯方回應：<br />\n社會服務令已經有一定阻嚇性，對於一個從事勞動工作的人來說，並不是輕柔的刑罰。第二，因案件變得普及，而追溯以前案件加刑以增加阻嚇性，有違法律原則，因為新的量刑指引應向後生效。<br />\n<br />\n另外，被告因本案而還柙12天，根據《監獄規則》不准許將實際刑期減至少於31天。若判處被告2個月即時監禁，扣除已執行的社會服務令時數及還柙日數，實質刑期會少於31天，因此刑期將不獲扣減，變相令被告白坐12天。<br />\n<br />\n📌<br />\n法庭認為梁震威案案發時附近有幾十人非法聚集，被告阻止警長上前截停有關人士。在朱家言案中，D2用手阻止警員作出拘捕，上訴後改判感化令。<br />\n<br />\n本案不涉及實質襲擊警員，亦沒有更多聚眾擾亂行為，亦無證供指被告與其他涉案人士情節有直接關係，情節比朱家言案及梁震威案更輕微。<br />\n<br />\n🟢維持原有判刑，可取回$12,000訟費<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\nReference ：<br />\nHCMA 496/2015 (<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=105516&amp;QS=%2B&amp;TP=JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fsearch%2Fsearch_result_detail_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D105516%26QS%3D%252B%26TP%3DJU&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YsvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=b19b23ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=105516&amp;QS=%2B&amp;TP=JU</a>) HKSAR v. 朱家言<br />\nHCMA152/2002 (<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=24615&amp;QS=%2B&amp;TP=JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fsearch%2Fsearch_result_detail_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D24615%26QS%3D%252B%26TP%3DJU&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YsvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=8b8c1ebc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=24615&amp;QS=%2B&amp;TP=JU</a>) HKSAR and LEUNG CHUN WAI SUNNY"},{"pid":"ae2d937d0d455a0056463f248f1474f80e1660e9","tid":2148615,"uid":277934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549d6b96ff2cdde0008ffe9e3e395a0bea468538","tid":2148615,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae2d937d0d455a0056463f248f1474f80e1660e9","tid":2148615,"uid":277934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3378bb8c875046b7902f59e9ddc22bdd4e55db08","tid":2148615,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /